No. D-2545. In the Matter of Discipline of William Craig Campbell, II. 562 U.S. 815, 131 S. Ct. 406,

178 L. Ed. 2d 270,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7532. October 4, 2010.

William Craig Campbell, II, of Saipan, Northern Mariana Islands, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him *271to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
